Title: A expectation which turned into hope
DateModified: '2018-02-19'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/a-expectation-which-turned-into-hope
SetInCountry: India
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Rushika Pithadia
AuthorCountry: India
Text: Argentina a country with beautiful people ,friendly local guides ,Argentina
  being a well known destination for adventure seekers ,a adventure cannot be completed
  alone,having a local resident is much more fun and enthusiastic to experience.the
  adventure with a local doesn't be limited with having adenture .Knowing their views
  thoughts is itself a adventure. A local is a best person to tell you what's the
  history and what's the real adventure in Argentina.
